  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Type</h2>This is a VR.RPG of realistic cool weapon battle experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/a2bedbf4161b05fb3d14c126f0654bab.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operation</h2>We redesigned the game vision, operation, movement, and interactive experience based on VR features.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/abd55be2ce8c05629b187ae3e15c17fb.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG system</h2>There are various RPG classic systems such as experience, level, currency, props, weapons, and skills. There are basic games such as weapon shop, war sand table, story level, and BOSS challenge. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/9ef49576a40d8a85fecf24336d7fe1b0.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/0ec322b335b46a76a2f19fbbc102fc14.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Egg white</h2>If you read the instructions carefully, the game still has an egg barrier.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/6777fdd65a900d3ea1a246e4e65152f3.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow-up</h2>Now is the basic game demo. We are trying to create a randomly generated level and monster system, and continue to enrich the game scene, monsters, bosses, weapons, and skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/43179e4cd1e4d36b2b8c3220b33ccefc.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Type</h2>This is a VR.RPG of realistic cool weapon battle experience.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/a2bedbf4161b05fb3d14c126f0654bab.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Operation</h2>We redesigned the game vision, operation, movement, and interactive experience based on VR features.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/abd55be2ce8c05629b187ae3e15c17fb.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RPG system</h2>There are various RPG classic systems such as experience, level, currency, props, weapons, and skills. There are basic games such as weapon shop, war sand table, story level, and BOSS challenge. <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/9ef49576a40d8a85fecf24336d7fe1b0.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/0ec322b335b46a76a2f19fbbc102fc14.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Egg white</h2>If you read the instructions carefully, the game still has an egg barrier.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/814900/extras/6777fdd65a900d3ea1a246e4e65152f3.avif?t=1548727388\" width=590 height=300 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Follow-up</h2>Now is the basic game demo. We are trying to create a randomly generated level and monster system, and continue to enrich the game scene, monsters, bosses, weapons, and skills.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.st